+ * - A pattern without a leading `/` matches at any depth in the tree.
+ * - A pattern *with* a leading `/` is matched relative to the gitignore file's
+ *   directory.
+ * - A pattern with a slash in the middle is also relative to the gitignore
+ *   directory.
+ * - Blank lines and lines starting with `#` are comments (handled by the
+ *   caller).
+ *
